snippet.title: UK: Mix it up with Pokémon Café Mix!
snippet.description:
What do you get when you combine puzzle games with the Pokemon Café? 

Get ready for #PokemonCafeMix, a free-to-start game coming to Nintendo Switch on June 24! https://bit.ly/3hEhUFq
